Summary
  Enables the label to scroll its text.
Description
  TJvLabelScroll enables a TJvBehaviorLabel to scroll its text.

  To use TJvLabelScroll capabilities with a TJvBehaviorLabel label, do the following:

  * Drop a TJvBehaviorLabel on a form.
  * Set <LINK TJvCustomBehaviorLabel.Behavior, Behavior> to 'Scrolling'.

  Do the following with the properties of property <LINK TJvCustomBehaviorLabel.BehaviorOptions,
